हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A shy schoolgirl secretly falls for her brother’s charming best friend, hiding her feelings for years. As they reunite years later, buried emotions resurface, igniting a tender yet forbidden romance. Watch "Hidden Love Surges" now!
